name: neon forest
description: A hypercolorized photograph of a forest in Berlin as my contribution for #OBJKT4OBJKT and #NFTsForAll #WorldArtDay2021 . My chosen theme is "Environment". Nature is the most wonderful work of art and my biggest inspiration to create. As humans, we are capable of making great things but we will never be able to outdo what the magic of life in our planet provides for us.
